cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the downlink subcarrier spacing to the invalid value 4 (valid values are 0-3 corresponding to 15kHz, 30kHz, 60kHz, 120kHz) will cause configuration parsing errors or invalid bandwidth calculations leading to system initialization failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將下行子載波間距設定為無效值 4（有效值為 0-3，對應 15kHz、30kHz、60kHz、120kHz）會導致配置解析錯誤或無效的帶寬計算，從而導致系統初始化失敗。
